1191
00:42:10,520 --> 00:42:11,679
That's more like it.

1192
00:42:12,839 --> 00:42:14,560
She's my granddaughter.

1193
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:16,520
Leaving her with anyone, I'd be uneasy.

1194
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:18,920
Let Mr. Jia come back

1195
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:20,359
and take care of his own daughter.

1196
00:42:20,799 --> 00:42:21,400
No more working.

1197
00:42:24,080 --> 00:42:24,520
Then…

1198
00:42:24,839 --> 00:42:25,639
Find someone immediately.

1199
00:42:25,799 --> 00:42:27,359
find someone immediately.

1200
00:42:29,199 --> 00:42:30,239
Little Watermelon,

1201
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:32,040
your mom wants

1202
00:42:32,040 --> 00:42:33,600
to find another nanny to take care of you

1203
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:36,080
together with grandma,

1204
00:42:36,080 --> 00:42:37,159
