1208
00:42:43,719 --> 00:42:45,880
Those rosy cheeks.

1209
00:42:46,440 --> 00:42:48,159
Breastfeeding is just so good,

1210
00:42:48,159 --> 00:42:49,319
right?

1211
00:42:50,520 --> 00:42:51,440
Our precious little one

1212
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:53,279
is growing up so healthy

1213
00:42:53,520 --> 00:42:55,080
and strong.

1214
00:42:55,440 --> 00:42:56,880
Such a good baby.

1215
00:42:57,480 --> 00:42:59,359
Grandma loves you so much.

